{"type":"message","id":"f3c68728","parentId":"4f25333a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:52:31.166Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ao90u9uoqc1f_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 3015\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1' new_len=1163\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1\r\n[master 9695750] pulse: 2026-03-24 145215\n 6 files changed, 180 insertions(+), 118 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 145215.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 145215.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 145114.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 145215 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified that hybrid scoring (CFIxFreq) is the next logical experiment, but no implementation exists yet to test whether score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) properly distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectory tokens.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"gentle-trail","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 3015\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1' new_len=1163\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1\r\n[master 9695750] pulse: 2026-03-24 145215\n 6 files changed, 180 insertions(+), 118 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 145215.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 145215.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 145114.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 145215 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified that hybrid scoring (CFIxFreq) is the next logical experiment, but no implementation exists yet to test whether score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) properly distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectory tokens.\r\n","name":"